snippet.title: Yuuwaku Office Renaika PS1 Game Opening Movie
snippet.description:
Opening movie of the PS1 Game Yuuwaku Office Renaika, a dating simulation game that was only released in Japan.

Movie 2 del juego de PS1 Yuuwaku Office Renaika, un dating simulation que sólo salió en Japón.

Game copyright: Takara (1998)

More information about the game here:
